There are at least three ways in which charging a price may lead to increased
 usage.
 The first is a 
\emph on
screening effect
\emph default
, whereby only people who really value the product will acquire the product
 (while those who do not intent to use it will be less likely to buy it).
 A second is more psychological in nature and conjectures that people are
